sequenceDiagram
  actor E as Editor
  participant UI as Research Panel
  participant API as Studio API
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant W as Laptop Worker
  participant A as Article Publisher
  participant S as SearXNG

  E->>UI: Click Start Research
  UI->>API: POST /api/stories/{story_id}/research/start
  API->>DB: Insert queued research job
  API-->>UI: Return job immediately
  W->>DB: Claim next queued job
  W->>DB: Load selected story candidate
  W->>A: Fetch lead article HTML
  alt Full article is readable
    A-->>W: Article HTML
    W->>W: Extract and clean readable text
  else Blocked, short, or paywalled
    A-->>W: Error or boilerplate
    W->>W: Fall back to RSS title and summary
  end
  opt SearXNG is configured
    W->>S: Search selected headline in news category
    S-->>W: Related coverage leads
    loop Up to research document limit
      W->>A: Fetch related article
      A-->>W: HTML or failure
      W->>W: Use readable text or search snippet fallback
    end
  end
  W->>W: Split documents into sentence claims and evidence
  W->>W: Extract entities, numbers, dates, and warnings
  W->>DB: Save source documents and research pack
  W->>DB: Move story to research_ready
  W->>DB: Mark job completed
  DB-->>UI: SSE job update triggers refresh
  UI->>API: GET /api/stories/{story_id}/research
  API->>DB: Load latest research pack
  DB-->>UI: Summary, sources, claims, entities, warnings
